==> Note that we are constantly making ongoing improvements and
additions to many molecular bands. Updates, improvements, and
corrections to the edition are posted in the "Database Updates" panel
located on the home page of the HITRAN website. When citing the
database, it is recommended to indicate if an updated version of the
HITRAN2020 edition was used.

Please e-mail us (info@hitran.org) a summary of any serious problems you encounter (or successes or suggestions).

